[package]
name = "hyprlock"
version = "0.1.0"
description = "hyprlock — lock screen; sources hyprmocha palette"

[[link]]
source = ".config/hypr/hyprlock.conf"
target = ".config/hypr/hyprlock.conf"

---

# hyprlock

One file. Sources `~/.config/hypr/mocha.conf` (the
`hyprmocha` package) at runtime — link that one too or the
`$mauve` / `$font` references fail to resolve. Bound to
`SUPER_SHIFT + ESCAPE` in hyprland.conf.

Shares `~/.config/hypr/`.
